title: Cosmonaut removed from SpaceX's Crew 12 mission for violating national security rules: report
description: Veteran cosmonaut Oleg Artemyev was taken off SpaceX's Crew 12 mission to the International Space Station after violating ITAR regulations, according to the Russian publication The Insider.
